pageProduct.name: Oral B Toothpaste 3D White Whitening Therapy Deep Clean with Charcoal 95g
pageProduct.description:
Information

Oral-B 3D White Whitening Therapy goes beyond whitening, it's therapy for your teeth.

The Active Mineral Complex helps to gently whiten by removing up to 95% of surface stains in 3 days.

Oral-B 3D White Whitening Therapy is enamel safe.

The fluoride formula helps to remineralise weakened enamel.

General Information

Oral-B 3DWhite Whitening Therapy Deep Clean Charcoal 95G.

This 3DWhite Whitening Therapy formula contains an Active Mineral Complex and Charcoal.

Size: 95g

KEY FEATURES

• Purifies teeth by removing surface stains for a Whiter, Cleaner Smile.
• Removes surface stains and discolouration, strengthens enamel, and freshens breath.
• Invigorating Mint.

Warnings

Do not swallow. Do not use this product in children 6 years of age or less. In case of intake of fluoride from other source, consult a dentist or doctor. Contains Sodium fluoride.

Ingredients

Water, Sorbitol, Hydrated Silica, Disodium Pyrophosphate, Sodium Lauryl Sulfate, Flavour, Cellulose Gum, Sodium Hydroxide, Sodium Saccharin, Sodium Fluoride, Carbomer, Charcoal Powder, Polysorbate 80, CI 77891, CI 77019.

Directions

Apply the product onto a soft bristled toothbrush. Brush teeth thoroughly at least twice a day (morning and evening) or as recommended by a dentist.
